# Architecture & Patterns

## Framework & Runtime

<!-- Source: payments-api (repo) -->
### Use Fastify as HTTP framework
This project uses Fastify ^4.26.0. All HTTP servers and API endpoints must use Fastify. Do not use Express, Koa, or other HTTP frameworks.

## Data Access Patterns

<!-- Source: payments-api (repo) -->
### Use Prisma ORM for database access
All database queries must go through Prisma. Use the repository pattern — never write raw SQL in route handlers or service functions.

